messages.messageBody:
I really need your help. My daughter, in her final year at Rutgers, is
doing a paper on Homeschoolers...that's all I know about it. She herself was
homeschooled for the last three years of highschool. She would like to talk
with Highland Park NJ homeschoolers of all ilks. If anyone is from Highland
Park, and would like to participate, or knows someone from Highland Park who
may be interested, please have them mail me at
hindar@...
putting HIGHLAND PARK in the subject heading. Please add a contact number.
My daughter will be in touch with you. If someone has responded and I
missed it, I apologize. I have been ill for the past two weeks. Found out I
had bronchitis....

be well,
Rachel Ann






[Non-text portions of this message have been removed]
